@DATABASE "Robocop II"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - R - Robocop II"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - R
                   ====================================

                                Robocop II
                                ==========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38765,0)"}          38765,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(27587,128) zxampoke(27587,128)"}          27587,x (x= 1-128)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
